Voiceflow Responsibilities

Voiceflow is responsible for:

Starting conversations
Collecting user messages
Calling Flask APIs
Showing AI responses
Managing conversation flow
Displaying chatbot UI

Voiceflow does not replace Flask or Gemini.

==========


What Does Flask Do?

Flask handles:

Business logic
API endpoints
Gemini communication
Order processing
Google Sheets integration

=========

Voiceflow vs Flask
-------------------
| Voiceflow           | Flask              |
| ------------------- | ------------------ |
| Conversation Design | Backend Logic      |
| Chat Interface      | Python Programming |
| API Calls           | API Creation       |
| Variables           | Business Logic     |
| User Flow           | AI Integration     |


